<h3>Response</h3>
<p><em>Every request in this section returns this: </em></p>
<pre><code class="language-json">
{
	"_id": "64090df9e0408659f3185eda",
	"content": "hello world",
	"date": "2023-03-08T22:36:29.834Z",
	"author": "64012c17ee606bf7649fad84",
	"conversation": "64090daecbd947e2e4895cf6",
	"__v": 0,
	"status": "sent"
}
</code></pre>
<p>
	`status` can be either 'sent', 'recieved' or 'deleted'
</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/messages/{id}</code></h3>
<p>Returns the specified message if it has access to it</p>

<h3><strong>GET</strong> <code>/api/messages/conversation/{id}</code></h3>
<p>Returns an array with all the messages from a conversation this user has access to</p>

<h3><strong>POST</strong> <code>/api/messages/</code></h3>
<p>Sends a new message</p>
<h4>Request body</h4>
<ul>
  <li><strong>conversation</strong>: ID of the conversation</li>
  <li><strong>content</strong>: The body of the message</li>
</ul>
